<td valign="top" style="padding-right:30px; padding-left:20px;">
<div id="Idea_2748"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/2748-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_2748">Direct agencies to use online communications tools to help resolve disputes over FOIA requests.&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/3967-4049">Sunshine in Government Initiative </a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">10 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">Direct agencies to use online communications tools to help resolve disputes over FOIA requests, including internal agency appeals processes and through mediation provided by the new Office of Government Information Services (OGIS). </div>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaFooter"><span style="border-right: 1px solid silver; margin:0 10px 0 0; padding: 0 5px 0 0; color: #666;"><a id="DiscussionTopic_2748" href="javascript:ajaxLink('DiscussionTopicComment_2748', '/akira/discussion.do?mode=comment&dbid=2237&topicID=2748')">Comments (0)</a></span><span id="DiscussionTopicTag_2748"><a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?discussionID=2237">Making Government Operations More Open</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=foia">foia</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=ogis">ogis</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=online dispute resolution">online dispute resolution</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=mediation">mediation</a></span></div><div style="margin-top:3px;" id="DiscussionTopicComment_2748"></div>
